---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="How it works">
  <Container>
    <section class="pt-16 pb-4 md:pt-20 md:pb-6">
      <div class="text-center mt-8 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#1D1D1F] mb-3">How it works</h1>
        <p class="text-[#6B6F76] text-base md:text-lg">
          Build, publish, test, and get insights in one loop.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        {/* Step 1 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-[#F9FAFB] rounded-lg border border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#3D78B0] text-white flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold">
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-[#1D1D1F] text-lg mb-1">Publish your prototype</h2>
            <p class="text-[#6B6F76] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Drag and drop a static build, paste a Figma prototype link, or let your AI agent publish via the Aero MCP server. Every publish gets a live, permanent URL. Previous versions stay accessible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 2 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-[#F9FAFB] rounded-lg border border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#3D78B0] text-white flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold">
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-[#1D1D1F] text-lg mb-1">Run a user test on it</h2>
            <p class="text-[#6B6F76] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Create a test on the same URL you just published. Define the tasks you want real people to try. Share the test link. Aero records each session: screen and microphone, so you see exactly what happened and hear what testers thought.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Step 3 */}
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6 bg-[#F9FAFB] rounded-lg border border-[rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#3D78B0] text-white flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold">
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-semibold text-[#1D1D1F] text-lg mb-1">Get AI insights back to your agent</h2>
            <p class="text-[#6B6F76] text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Aero transcribes every session and runs AI analysis across all recordings. The findings are available as a structured summary your agent can read via MCP. Your agent sees what to fix and can immediately publish the next iteration.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>
